data.description: This charming one-story, 3 bdrm, 2 bath ranch home, nestled in the heart of Great Bridge, offers the perfect blend of comfort and style.  Step into the bright and sunny kitchen, complete with updated cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and stunning granite countertops. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the cozy living area, featuring a warm fireplace and custom built-ins that add a touch of sophistication. The den also comes with additional storage with more built-ins. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated to create a spa-like retreat. Outside, you'll find a large backyard, perfect for entertaining friends and family or enjoying peaceful moments of relaxation. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours. Welcome to a life of comfort and convenience! (paint on exterior fireplace has been completed)
